text: Sven Palle Sørensen (23 November 1898 - 9 January 1978) was a Danish diver. He competed at the 1920 Summer Olympics and the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1898 births Category:1978 deaths Category:Danish male divers Category:Olympic divers of Denmark Category:Divers at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen
